{"tid":2325033,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！由於供過於求原因，Tesla 暫停部份生產線","createTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T10:31:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cdba50fcc4515017aa699b660e71d99bbe533639","tid":2325033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"最近有消息指 Tesla 將會暫停部分的 Model S 和 X 生產線，調整產能。<br />\n據報導指，Tesla 最近向其加州 Fremont 工廠的工作人員發出電郵，預告他們將會在 12 月 24 日到明年 1 月 11 日之間暫停 Model S 和 Model X 的生產線。在這些生產線工作的員工，其中一星期將會是全額有薪假期和公衆假，剩下的日子將會變成無薪假，但就可以申請擔任工廠其他職務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/13/tesla-model-s-and-x-production-will-shut-down-for-18-days/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2Ftesla-model-s-and-x-production-will-shut-down-for-18-days%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=ae959d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/13/tesla-model-s-and-x-production-will-shut-down-for-18-days/life-tech/auto/</a>"},{"pid":"20ce13b9a54035472ff2e496339626a5dda97c0f","tid":2325033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7006cf53542d098bd5137302c825afe293fbc50d","tid":2325033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"冇人買"},{"pid":"d76e24c51df60d975278b4a166941d5050d15d82","tid":2325033,"uid":366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"400收tsla股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" clas